title: [Ta'Illistim, Mzaarine Wey]
description: A tall stonework wall stands on the west side of the wey, tiny chinks between the massive stone blocks barely visible to the eye.  Fragrant white climbing roses, their clusters of blooms drifting in the night breeze, climb portions of the wall and hang gracefully from the top of the granite edifice.
